者本惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果呢個世間既設定唔會因為食物同資源影響到生存機會同生活質素，生物就唔需要誰大誰惡誰正確<br />\n話雖如此，人類有超越動物既思想，能力愈大責任愈大，好應該盡力將呢個世間本來就險惡既設定消除"},{"pid":"765e32a84398cf71fc0865b02c7cb716e99f103b","tid":1087715,"uid":245399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T22:47:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jIXPGk1GhWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjIXPGk1GhWA&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi34IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=a5f50768\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jIXPGk1GhWA</a>"}]}